body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to XYZ Solutions. My name is Aaron Robinson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Olivia Wood.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Olivia. Could you please provide me with your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's the tenth of May, one nine eight five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. And can you also share your home address with me?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course. It's three four five Maple Street, Apartment two zero zero, Cityville.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for sharing that information, Olivia. We'll make sure to keep it secure. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling excited! I wanted to inquire about the data management services offered for car dealerships.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: That's fantastic to hear, Olivia! Our data management solutions can definitely help streamline your processes. Thank you for considering us. If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. Thank you for your time today, Olivia.
